Means for beta oscillations

Ampl SmN

Amplitude signal minus noise (SmN)

plots

iv = "AmpSmN"
Dtmp = getdiffs_SIV_s1(DSIV_s1, iv = iv)
myylim = c(-0.5, 0.5)#max(Dtmp)) 
Dtmp = Dtmp[,c(3:5)]#[,c(10:27)]
Dtmp = cbind(DSIV_s1$fp, Dtmp)
colnames(Dtmp)[1] =  c('fp', 'low', 'high', 'high-low')

Dtmp2 = getdiffs_SIV_s2(DSIV_s2, iv = iv)
myylim = c(-0.5, 0.5)#max(Dtmp2)) 
Dtmp2 = Dtmp2[,c(4:9)]#[,c(10:27)]
Dtmp2 = cbind(DSIV_s2$fp, Dtmp2)
colnames(Dtmp2)[1] =  c('fp', 'no', 'low', 'high', 'low-no','high-no','high-low')

bp1a = plotoverlay(dm = Dtmp,lbl = paste0("ASSR study 1"), dvy = "Mean SmN amplitude (V)", myylim)
bp1b = plotoverlay(dm = Dtmp2,lbl = paste0("ASSR study 2"), dvy = "", myylim)

grid.arrange(bp1a, bp1b, ncol = 3)

bp1 = arrangeGrob(bp1a, bp1b, ncol = 2)
ggsave(file.path(dir_fig,"figure_amp_beta_ASSRStudy1and2.jpg"), bp1, dpi = 600, width = 5, height = 4)
ggsave(file.path(dir_fig,"figure_amp_beta_ASSRStudy1and2.pdf"), bp1, dpi = 600, width = 5, height = 4)



Dtmp3 = getdiffs_SV(DSV, iv = iv)
myylim = c(min(Dtmp3), max(Dtmp3)) 
Dtmp3 = Dtmp3[,c(10:27)]
Dtmp3 = cbind(DSV$fp, Dtmp3)

Dtmp3a = Dtmp3[,c(1,2:7)]
colnames(Dtmp3a) = c('fp', 'no', 'low', 'high', 'low-no', 'high-no', 'high-low')
bp3a = plotoverlay(dm = Dtmp3a,lbl = paste0("20 Hz"), dvy = "Mean SmN amplitude (V)", myylim)
Dtmp3b = Dtmp3[,c(1,8:13)]
colnames(Dtmp3b) = c('fp', 'no', 'low', 'high', 'low-no', 'high-no', 'high-low')
bp3b = plotoverlay(dm = Dtmp3b,lbl = paste0("40 Hz"), dvy = "", myylim)
Dtmp3c = Dtmp3[,c(1,14:19)]
colnames(Dtmp3c) = c('fp', 'no', 'low', 'high', 'low-no', 'high-no', 'high-low')
bp3c = plotoverlay(dm = Dtmp3c,lbl = paste0("80 Hz"), dvy = "", myylim)
grid.arrange(bp3a, bp3b, bp3c, ncol = 3)

bp3 = arrangeGrob(bp3a, bp3b, bp3c, ncol = 3)

ggsave(file.path(dir_fig,"figure_amp_beta_ASSR2.jpg"), bp3, dpi = 600, width = 7, height = 4)
ggsave(file.path(dir_fig,"figure_amp_beta_ASSR2.pdf"), bp3, dpi = 600, width = 7, height = 4)
